40:28.048 --> 40:58.020
about 200 missionaries and we want to give a little something to the husband and the wife and and to each of the children and we're gonna have in that room someone that can show medical attention to them or some opportunities for Christian counseling and and we want to minister to the missionaries then we have national pastors and Christian workers from over 50 countries registered to come to Manila in the second week of March and if you'll pray I'll be preaching the opening message on Monday night the closing Tuesday night closing message on Friday

40:58.000 --> 41:06.152
