But the first so kind of takes

43:41.456 --> 43:45.721
takes the point at the outreach and getting the gospel out into our community.

43:45.981 --> 43:49.324
And I hope that you'll be right there with the SOS Times on Saturdays.

43:49.605 --> 43:54.970
What a great response we have this past week and many visitors this day from that outreach as well.

43:54.990 --> 44:01.898
I'll let you read some of the other things here in the adult ministry, 125 adults through the continued discipleship program.

44:02.258 --> 44:10.307
And you can see some of these goals, seeing 100 new members in ministry service and getting folks involved in the connection groups, our children's ministry.

44:10.807 --> 44:11.428
Of course we want

