46:24.864 --> 46:43.200
We want to continue to see them advancing academically, of course, spiritually, improving our classroom technology as well, utilizing Google Chromebooks and Google Classroom software, improving the classroom facilities by upgrading the lighting flooring and common space area, and then launching Kids Corner Kindergarten in the fall.

