48:39.991 --> 48:45.956
But those are some high-end goals that we'd like you to pray with us about for the Ministry of West Coast Baptist

48:45.936 --> 48:46.437
college.

48:46.877 --> 48:48.539
Now a new year is like a gift.

48:48.799 --> 48:53.584
It's a gift from God, the fact that we're alive, the fact that we have the opportunity to serve Him.

48:53.985 --> 48:58.289
And I want to mention some resources to you to help you steward this new year that we've been given.

48:58.630 --> 49:04.596
So on the next page, if you would, let me mention some of these for the Williams, if you'd grab all these items down here for me while I continue speaking.

49:04.896 --> 49:07.359
You'll notice, first of all, the stewarding life planner.

49:07.679 --> 49:12.424
This is something that I've been using already this year, and it's not too late to begin using it.

49:12.464 --> 49:13.926
Today is January the 12th.

49:14.286 --> 49:15.908
Stewarding life planner is just some great

49:15.888 --> 49:27.020
material written on understanding God's purpose for your life, on how to be accountable with your goals, on developing a personal vision statement, on stewarding life in general.

49:27.560 --> 49:31.044
And it just helps you to outline some of the priorities for your year.

49:31.545 --> 49:45.860
Also, there is a section in the back that talks about leadership and influence and financial management and our identity in Christ, various different topics that are important in the carving out and planning of a successful new year.

49:45.840 --> 49:48.803
The heart of this really is just the daily devotional guide.

49:49.244 --> 49:51.526
Every day there's a Scripture reading recommendation.

49:51.586 --> 49:54.830
There's a Scripture at the bottom for meditation and memory.

49:55.150 --> 50:05.521
There's a place to mark down what Scripture you read, what God spoke to you about, what you can praise the Lord for, and then the areas of those priorities in your life that you're working on in that day.

50:05.861 --> 50:07.743
And this is something that I use every day.

50:07.803 --> 50:15.812
It's not a journal per se, but I do write down what God is speaking to me about and some of the things that He's impressing upon my heart.

50:15.792 --> 50:23.580
something like this, it might help you to be more concise and to be more intentional in your devotional life.

50:23.640 --> 50:26.123
And so I recommend the Stewarding Life Planner.

50:26.263 --> 50:28.085
It's available for you in the back.

50:28.405 --> 50:32.430
Also available in the back, we have some other items that might be of help to you.

50:33.050 --> 50:37.555
If you haven't used, for example, the Trust and Obey devotional, those are available there for you.

50:37.896 --> 50:41.479
Terry has a lady's devotional called It's a Wonderful Life Journal.

50:42.000 --> 50:45.764
Similar to the Stewarding Life Journal, yet there are some more

50:45.744 --> 50:52.274
more different ideas and devotional topics for the ladies as well as questions each day for your devotions.

50:52.574 --> 50:56.621
Also, you'll notice they're a Bible reading schedule that's available at the guest services.

50:56.981 --> 50:58.023
That's a free item.

50:58.323 --> 51:05.434
The daily in the word email, everywhere I go when I witness to different people, I mention this and I tell them, here's something you can look at.

51:05.454 --> 51:11.023
This can be emailed right to your computer and all of our members can take advantage of that.

51:11.363 --> 51:13.266
It's an encouragement.

51:13.346 --> 51:16.275
How many of you, the world, pop it up stuff in your computer?

51:17.318 --> 51:18.923
They're telling you buy this, do that.

51:19.204 --> 51:22.354
How many of you think they're listening to you as you talk about it at home, right?

51:23.362 --> 51:24.743
Have you ever talked about something?

51:24.763 --> 51:26.885
And a few minutes later, boom, it comes up, right?

51:27.265 --> 51:29.908
I'm just here to tell you, the world is bombarding us.

51:30.108 --> 51:34.392
You ought to set yourself this year so that you've got some spiritual reminders coming.

51:34.412 --> 51:37.134
And if you don't have daily in the word, that'll be a tremendous help to you.

51:37.454 --> 51:42.298
The Lancaster Baptist app, if you haven't downloaded that on your smartphone, let me encourage you to do that.

51:42.659 --> 51:45.221
And the Great Commission app is another app.

51:45.501 --> 51:47.463
It's just a tremendous soul-winning opportunity.

51:48.003 --> 51:51.767
I know sometimes for me, I try to keep tracks in a couple spots in my car, in my briefcase.

51:52.087 --> 51:53.348
